# AI Resume Analyzer

AI-powered resume analyzer that evaluates resumes based on job roles and provides improvement suggestions.

## Features

- Resume scoring system
- AI skill detection
- ATS compatibility analysis
- Resume improvement suggestions
- Role-based evaluation
- JWT authentication

## Tech Stack

Frontend
- React
- CSS animations

Backend
- .NET Web API
- Repository Pattern
- JWT Authentication
- SQL Server

## How It Works

1. Upload resume
2. AI analyzes skills and structure
3. Resume score is generated
4. Suggestions provided to improve resume

